}
.table_shade .even {
    background: #FBFBFB;
}
</style>
<p>
<p>Para <span class="math inline">\(Z=(X-1)/2\)</span>, sabendo que <span class="math inline">\(E(X)=1\)</span> e <span class="math inline">\(\operatorname{DP}(X)=2\)</span>, quais são <span class="math inline">\(E(Z)\)</span> e <span class="math inline">\(\operatorname{Var}(Z)\)</span>?</p>
</p>]]></text>
</questiontext>
<generalfeedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<p>Pela linearidade, <span class="math inline">\(E(Z)=[E(X)-\mu]/\sigma=0\)</span>. Além disso,
<span class="math inline">\(\operatorname{Var}(Z)=\operatorname{Var}(X)/\sigma^2=1\)</span>.</p>
</p>]]></text>
</generalfeedback>
<penalty>0</penalty>
<defaultgrade>1</defaultgrade>
<shuffleanswers>false</shuffleanswers>
<single>true</single>
<answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(E(Z)=0.5\)</span> e <span class="math inline">\(\operatorname{Var}(Z)=1/4\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(E(Z)=1\)</span> e <span class="math inline">\(\operatorname{Var}(Z)=0\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(E(Z)=0\)</span> e <span class="math inline">\(\operatorname{Var}(Z)=4\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="100" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(E(Z)=0\)</span> e <span class="math inline">\(\operatorname{Var}(Z)=1\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(E(Z)=1\)</span> e <span class="math inline">\(\operatorname{Var}(Z)=2\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
</question>


